^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The bidding was ok. With a weak hand, it is usually better to play in the weak hand's long suit. I am not sure even 2D makes. Had I rebid 2D, we end up losing at least 2 clubs, 2H, and 1S. And with no entries to sandy's hand I cannot  take any finesses so I lose probably at least 2 diamonds. Therefore, even had I bid 2 diamonds, it is  probably the same result or even worse.|
